data.description: Welcome to Island Living! The seller is offering a $10,000 credit towards rate buy down or closing costs! The home features a new roof, windows, interior paint & kitchen counters, interior shades & more! Step into the open-concept living area, boasting high ceilings and abundant natural light. The spacious living room with a cozy fireplace flows seamlessly into the dining area, creating the perfect ambiance for family gatherings. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and ample storage. The master suite offers a retreat with a private ensuite bath and a walk-in closet, while additional bedrooms provide versatility for an office, guests or family members.
